      <title>苹果家居设备、汽车老手退出 Rivian 顶级产品职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/apple-home-devices-car-veteran-exits-for-top-rivian-product-role</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位负责领导家庭设备工作并帮助开始开发电动汽车的苹果公司资深人士即将前往 Rivian Automotive Inc.，这标志着这家 iPhone 制造商的又一次高层离职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/apple-home-devices-car-veteran-exits-for-top-rivian-product-role</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 00:15:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国计划于三月底宣布为芯片厂提供巨额拨款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/us-set-to-announce-big-grants-for-chip-factories-by-end-of-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，美国计划在 3 月底之前宣布重大芯片拨款，为向半导体制造商提供数十亿美元资金以增强国内生产铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/us-set-to-announce-big-grants-for-chip-factories-by-end-of-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 18:32:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ISS 表示和利时股东应拒绝 Ascendent 的要约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/iss-says-hollysys-shareholders-should-reject-ascendent-s-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[机构股东服务公司 (Institutional Shareholder Services Inc.) 建议和利时自动化技术有限公司 (Hollysys Automation Technologies Ltd.) 的股东拒绝私募股权公司 Ascendent Capital Partners 提出的 16.6 亿美元收购提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/iss-says-hollysys-shareholders-should-reject-ascendent-s-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 17:37:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的 X 承诺在德克萨斯州设立 100 人的办公室来监管内容</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/musk-s-x-pledges-100-person-office-in-texas-to-police-content</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 旗下的 X 公司（前身为 Twitter）正计划在德克萨斯州奥斯汀建立一个新的“信任与安全卓越中心”，以帮助执行其内容和安全规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/musk-s-x-pledges-100-person-office-in-texas-to-police-content</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 16:44:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联航准备恢复波音 737 Max 9 喷气客机的航班</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/united-poised-to-resume-boeing-max-9-flights-after-grounding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合航空控股公司 (United Airlines Holdings Inc.) 准备从周日开始恢复部分波音公司 Max 9 飞机的服务，几周前，阿拉斯加航空公司 (Alaska Airlines) 的一架航班在空中因门塞爆裂而导致这些飞机停飞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/united-poised-to-resume-boeing-max-9-flights-after-grounding</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 16:40:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《华尔街日报》称拜登预计将宣布数十亿美元的芯片补贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/biden-expected-to-announce-billions-in-chip-subsidies-wsj-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》报道，拜登政府预计将很快宣布向英特尔公司和台积电等芯片制造商提供数十亿美元的新补贴，作为回流生产努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/biden-expected-to-announce-billions-in-chip-subsidies-wsj-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 11:31:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股的崛起推动欧洲蓝筹股指数发生根本性变化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/asml-and-sap-lead-tech-s-rise-in-europe-as-blue-chip-index-scales-23-year-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在华尔街股票破纪录的阴影下度过了数十年之后，欧元区蓝筹股指数的转型似乎最终为基准设定了新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/asml-and-sap-lead-tech-s-rise-in-europe-as-blue-chip-index-scales-23-year-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果解决了影响应用商店和音乐应用的服务中断问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/apple-suffers-service-outage-that-hits-app-store-and-music-app</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Apple Inc. 解决了影响其 App Store、音乐应用程序和购买 AppleCare 支持的能力的服务中断，从而扰乱了一些客户的几种流行产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/apple-suffers-service-outage-that-hits-app-store-and-music-app</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 00:47:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰勒·斯威夫特、乔·拜登、《死孩子》：假人工智能内容泛滥</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/taylor-swift-joe-biden-dead-kids-fake-ai-content-floods-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本月，人工智能生成的深度造假在社交媒体上激增，造成一系列知名受害者死亡，并在美国大选周期即将到来之前将受操纵媒体的风险提升到公众讨论中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-27/taylor-swift-joe-biden-dead-kids-fake-ai-content-floods-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 00:23:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Airbnb 在国际推送中增加货币兑换费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/airbnb-adds-currency-conversion-fee-amid-international-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着度假租赁公司进军更多国际市场以促进增长，爱彼迎 (Airbnb Inc.) 计划提高跨币种预订的宾客服务费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/airbnb-adds-currency-conversion-fee-amid-international-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 17:06:41 GMT</pubDate>
